Starcraft Corp to buy National Mobility . Starcraft Corp said Wednesday it reached an agreement to acquire National Mobility Corp for an undisclosed price . National Mobility makes conversion vehicles for the physically challenged , posting annual sales of more than $ 5 million , Starcraft said . Starcraft manufatures second - stage van , truck and sport utility conversions through three divisions . Its shares were up 1 / 8 Wednesday afternoon at 4 - 5 / 8 . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
